{"tid":436871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄰國人風暴下非法露營被困 獲水警安排專人接送","createTime":"2017-10-15T13:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T03:13:49.000Z","uid":136994,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c7883d70ed62743e37ca1543877379b9b85c45a3","tid":436871,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T13:20:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171015/57334802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171015%2F57334802&d=zb2WF1gw%2FswQ8xG6zdEI2XIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c8213559\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171015%2F57334802&h=f8f3baaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171015/57334802</a><br />\n<br />\n中午12時半許，10名內地男女在西貢橋咀島露營(兩日一夜)，因風暴關係街渡停開被困島上，眾人斷水斷糧報警求助。警方派出水警輪協助，並聯絡區內船家趕赴現場接載被困男女。<br />\n<br />\n直至傍晚6時許，警方再接獲有12人報稱於橋咀島被困需要救援，水警正趕往現場。<br />\n<br />\n被困內地人分別5男5女，年齡介乎21至57歲，其中有8名較年青的來自深圳，另有兩人來自湖北，他們沒有受傷，乘搭街渡返回西貢碼頭後，再坐小巴出市區。<br />\n<br />\n其中來自湖北的女遊客稱，今次是第一次來港旅遊，昨日到橋咀島前已獲悉有風暴，但因為從未遇過颱風，所以不知道風暴的威力，亦不知道在風暴期間沒有街渡服務。有被困內地客亦稱，只帶備一天的食水到島上，求救前已斷水斷糧，因沒有方法聯絡其他船家，所以報警求助，待救期間到廁所避風雨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例，任何人只可以喺郊野公園內指定露營地點露營，否則即屬違法。下面張地圖清楚顯示，橋咀島並無任何指定露營地點，紮營即屬違法。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/country/cou_vis/cou_vis_cam/cou_vis_cam_cam/files/M_MC_2015_072_AllCampSite.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.afcd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fcountry%2Fcou_vis%2Fcou_vis_cam%2Fcou_vis_cam_cam%2Ffiles%2FM_MC_2015_072_AllCampSite.jpg&h=4db87052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解班鄰國人可以凌駕法律，唔使比人告，仲有VIP級待遇，知唔知八號風球下仲要船家救你地真係好牙煙㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己Google下，你就會知好多人真係試過喺指定露營地點外露營而比人告，罰款都要幾嚿水<br />\n<br />\n香港政府比人鬧唔係無原因㗎，對香港人就執正嚟做，鄰國人就輕輕放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91fd9b9d78146962c369c963f22dd4d61e227645","tid":436871,"uid":30768,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T13:31:02.000Z","msg":"政府今次做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493fa11d2112e0c04566fa5571bc69274dc3fea3","tid":436871,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T13:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府今次做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雲格好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bf34259eba676e01f871781f87a83d6367185f","tid":436871,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"奶共正苦只識對香港人下毒手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa6b94e1a744292aa3f2a38d1eb51330212b024","tid":436871,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"唔知風暴威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔講以為深圳喺內陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a0a208f1d6b50ab7e1383266bef60a5d5567b4","tid":436871,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T13:40:43.000Z","msg":"香港政府比人鬧唔係無原因㗎，對香港人就執正嚟做，鄰國人就輕輕放過<br />\n<br />\n就係要話俾你班港喱聽邊個係宗主國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0daa72d3c33c094dc262e89fa8dbb46aaba63f4","tid":436871,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T13:41:46.000Z","msg":"另外十個係武漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388ff21692c4e0bea4d06dbb3d2d1327e37d1f6e","tid":436871,"uid":55,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc